msgstr "Criar um cluster downstream definindo recursos da CAPI"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:115
msgid ""
"This guide assumes an existing RKE2 cluster and Rancher (including "
"cert-manager) has been installed, for example by using Edge Image Builder "
"(<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Este guia considera que já existe um cluster RKE2 e que o Rancher (incluindo "
