#: l10n/source/edge.xml:129
msgid ""
"After some time, the controller pods should be running in the "
"<literal>capi-system</literal>, <literal>capm3-system</literal>, "
"<literal>rke2-bootstrap-system</literal> and "
"<literal>rke2-control-plane-system</literal> namespaces."
msgstr ""
"Após algum tempo, os pods do controlador deverão estar em execução nos "
"namespaces <literal>capi-system</literal>, <literal>capm3-system</literal>, "
"<literal>rke2-bootstrap-system</literal> e <literal>rke2-control-plane-"
"system</literal>."

