#: l10n/source/edge.xml:134
msgid ""
"Please follow <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> first to build "
"a fresh image as the first step required to create clusters."
msgstr ""
"Primeiro siga o <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> para gerar "
"uma imagem nova como a primeira etapa necessária para criar clusters."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:135 l10n/source/edge.xml:3372 l10n/source/edge.xml:3420
msgid ""
"When running Edge Image Builder, a directory is mounted from the host, so it "
"is necessary to create a directory structure to store the configuration "
"files used to define the target image."
msgstr ""
"Ao executar o Edge Image Builder, um diretório é montado com base no host, "
"portanto, é necessário criar uma estrutura de diretórios para armazenar os "
"arquivos de configuração usados para definir a imagem de destino."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:136 l10n/source/edge.xml:3373
msgid ""
"<literal>downstream-cluster-config.yaml</literal> is the image definition "
"file, see <xref linkend=\"quickstart-eib\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"<literal>downstream-cluster-config.yaml</literal> é o arquivo de definição "
"da imagem. Consulte o <xref linkend=\"quickstart-eib\"/> para obter mais "
"detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:137
msgid ""
"The base image when downloaded is <literal>xz</literal> compressed, which "
"must be uncompressed with <literal>unxz</literal> and copied/moved under the "
"<literal>base-images</literal> folder."
msgstr ""
"Quando o download da imagem base é feito, ela é compactada com <literal>xz</"
"literal>, que deve ser descompactada com <literal>unxz</literal> e copiada/"
"movida para a pasta <literal>base-images</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:138
msgid ""
"The <literal>network</literal> folder is optional, see <xref "
"linkend=\"metal3-add-network-eib\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"A pasta <literal>network</literal> é opcional. Consulte a <xref linkend="
"\"metal3-add-network-eib\"/> para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:139
msgid ""
"The custom/scripts directory contains scripts to be run on first-boot; "
