#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1075
msgid "Using the Rancher UI extension"
msgstr "Usando a extensão de IU do Rancher"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1076
msgid ""
"SUSE Edge Virtualization provides a UI extension for Rancher Manager, "
"enabling basic virtual machine management using the Rancher dashboard UI."
msgstr ""
"O SUSE Edge Virtualization oferece uma extensão de IU para o Rancher "
"Manager, que permite o gerenciamento básico de máquinas virtuais usando a "
"interface de usuário do Rancher Dashboard."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1078
msgid ""
"See Rancher Dashboard Extensions (<xref "
"linkend=\"components-rancher-dashboard-extensions\"/>) for installation "
"guidance."
msgstr ""
"Consulte as extensões do Rancher Dashboard (<xref linkend=\"components-"
"rancher-dashboard-extensions\"/>) para obter orientação de instalação."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1079
msgid "Using KubeVirt Rancher Dashboard Extension"
msgstr "Usando a extensão KubeVirt do Rancher Dashboard"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1080
msgid ""
"The extension introduces a new <emphasis role=\"strong\">KubeVirt</emphasis> "
"section to the Cluster Explorer. This section is added to any managed "
"cluster which has KubeVirt installed."
msgstr ""
"A extensão introduz uma nova seção <emphasis role=\"strong\">KubeVirt</"
"emphasis> no explorador de clusters, que é adicionada a qualquer cluster "
"gerenciado que tenha o KubeVirt instalado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1081
msgid ""
"The extension allows you to directly interact with KubeVirt Virtual Machine "
"resources to manage Virtual Machines lifecycle."
msgstr ""
"A extensão permite interagir diretamente com os recursos de máquina virtual "
"do KubeVirt para gerenciar o ciclo de vida das máquinas virtuais."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1082
msgid "Creating a virtual machine"
msgstr "Criando uma máquina virtual"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1083
msgid ""
"Navigate to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Cluster Explorer</emphasis> clicking "
"KubeVirt-enabled managed cluster in the left navigation."
msgstr ""
"Navegue até o <emphasis role=\"strong\">explorador de clustersr</emphasis> "
"clicando no cluster gerenciado habilitado para KubeVirt na navegação "
