#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1437
msgid ""
"The <literal>kubernetes</literal> section is optional, and it defines the "
"Kubernetes type and version. We are going to use the RKE2 distribution. Use "
"<literal>kubernetes.version: v1.32.4+k3s1</literal> if K3s is desired "
"instead. Unless explicitly configured via the "
"<literal>kubernetes.nodes</literal> field, all clusters we bootstrap in this "
"guide will be single-node ones."
msgstr ""
"A seção <literal>kubernetes</literal> é opcional e define o tipo e a versão "
"do Kubernetes. Vamos usar a distribuição RKE2. Em vez disso, se você "
"preferir o K3s, use <literal>kubernetes.version: v1.32.4+k3s1</literal>. "
"Exceto se claramente configurado no campo <literal>kubernetes.nodes</"
"literal>, todos os clusters que inicializamos neste guia são de nó único."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1438
msgid ""
"The <literal>embeddedArtifactRegistry</literal> section will include all "
"images which are only referenced and pulled at runtime for the specific "
