"<literal>UpgradePlan</literal>. Para saber todas as configurações possíveis, "
"consulte a <xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-extensions-upgrade-"
"plan\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1782
