"É criado um serviço diferente dependendo do tipo de upgrade que o sistema "
"operacional requer de uma versão do Edge para outra:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1831 l10n/source/edge.xml:2339
msgid ""
"For Edge versions that require the same OS version "
"(e.g. <literal>6.0</literal>), the <literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal> "
"will be created. It uses <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\">transactional-update</link> "
"to perform a <link "
"xl:href=\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">normal "
"package upgrade</link>."
msgstr ""
"Para versões do Edge que requerem a mesma versão de sistema operacional (por "
"exemplo, <literal>6.0</literal>), o <literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal> "
"é criado. Ele usa o <link xl:href=\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/"
"man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\">transactional-update</link> para "
"fazer <link xl:href="
"\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">upgrade de um "
"pacote normal</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1832 l10n/source/edge.xml:2340
msgid ""
"For Edge versions that require an OS version migration (e.g "
"<literal>6.0</literal> → <literal>6.1</literal>), the "
"<literal>os-migration.service</literal> will be created. It uses <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\">transactional-update</link> "
"to perform:"
msgstr ""
"Para versões do Edge que requerem a migração da versão de sistema "
"operacional (por exemplo, <literal>6.0</literal> → <literal>6.1</literal>), "
"o <literal>os-migration.service</literal> é criado. Ele usa o <link xl:href="
"\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8."
"html\">transactional-update</link> para fazer o seguinte:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1833 l10n/source/edge.xml:2341
msgid ""
"A <link "
"xl:href=\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">normal "
"package upgrade</link> which ensures that all packages are at up-to-date in "
"order to mitigate any failures in the migration related to old package "
"versions."
msgstr ""
"O <link xl:href="
"\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">upgrade de "
"pacote normal</link>, que garante que todos os pacotes sejam atualizados "
"para mitigar falhas na migração relacionadas a versões antigas dos pacotes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1834 l10n/source/edge.xml:2342
msgid ""
"An OS migration by utilizing the <literal>zypper migration</literal> "
"command."
msgstr ""
"A migração de sistema operacional usando o comando <literal>zypper "
"migration</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1835
msgid ""
"The services mentioned above are shipped on each node through a <literal>SUC "
"plan</literal> which must be located on the management cluster that is in "
"need of an OS upgrade."
msgstr ""
"Os serviços mencionados acima são distribuídos para cada nó por meio de um "
"<literal>plano do SUC</literal>, que deve estar localizado no cluster de "
"gerenciamento que precisa do upgrade de sistema operacional."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1836 l10n/source/edge.xml:1954
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2189 l10n/source/edge.xml:2344
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2459 l10n/source/edge.xml:2685
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Visão geral"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1837
msgid ""
"The upgrade of the operating system for management cluster nodes is done by "
"utilizing <literal>Fleet</literal> and the <literal>System Upgrade "
"Controller (SUC)</literal>."
msgstr ""
"O upgrade do sistema operacional para nós de cluster de gerenciamento é "
"feito pelo <literal>Fleet</literal> e pelo <literal>System Upgrade "
"Controller (SUC)</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1838 l10n/source/edge.xml:2346
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fleet</emphasis> is used to deploy and manage "
"<literal>SUC plans</literal> onto the desired cluster."
msgstr ""
"O <emphasis role=\"strong\">Fleet</emphasis> é usado para implantar e "
"gerenciar os <literal>planos do SUC</literal> no cluster desejado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1839 l10n/source/edge.xml:2347
msgid ""
"<literal>SUC plans</literal> are <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\">custom "
"resources</link> that describe the steps that <literal>SUC</literal> needs "
"to follow in order for a specific task to be executed on a set of nodes. For "
"an example of how an <literal>SUC plan</literal> looks like, refer to the "
"<link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">upstream "
"repository</link>."
msgstr ""
"Os <literal>planos do SUC</literal> são <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/"
"\">recursos personalizados</link> que descrevem as etapas que o "
"<literal>SUC</literal> precisa seguir para execução de uma tarefa específica "
"em um conjunto de nós. Para ver um exemplo de como é um <literal>plano do "
"SUC</literal>, consulte o <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-"
"upgrade-controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">repositório "
"upstream</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1840 l10n/source/edge.xml:2348
msgid ""
"The <literal>OS SUC plans</literal> are shipped to each cluster by deploying "
"a <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</link> or "
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">Bundle</link> resource "
"to a specific Fleet <link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/namespaces#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">workspace</link>. "
"Fleet retrieves the deployed <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> and deploys "
"its contents (the <literal>OS SUC plans</literal>) to the desired "
"cluster(s)."
msgstr ""
"Os <literal>planos do SUC de sistema operacional</literal> são enviados a "
"cada cluster por meio da implantação de um recurso <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</link> ou <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">Bundle</link> em um <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/namespaces#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-"
"clustergroups\">espaço de trabalho</link> do Fleet específico. O Fleet "
"recupera o <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> implantado e implanta seu "
"conteúdo (os <literal>planos do SUC de sistema operacional</literal>) no(s) "
"cluster(s) desejado(s)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1841 l10n/source/edge.xml:1959
msgid ""
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> resources are always deployed on the "
"<literal>management cluster</literal>. Whether to use a "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> or <literal>Bundle</literal> resource depends on "
"your use-case, check <xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Os recursos <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> sempre são implantados no "
"<literal>cluster de gerenciamento</literal>. O uso do recurso "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> ou <literal>Bundle</literal> depende do seu caso "
"de uso. Consulte a <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\""
"/> para obter mais informações."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1842 l10n/source/edge.xml:2350
msgid "<literal>OS SUC plans</literal> describe the following workflow:"
msgstr ""
"Os <literal>planos do SUC de sistema operacional</literal> descrevem o "
"seguinte fluxo de trabalho:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1843 l10n/source/edge.xml:2351
msgid ""
"Always <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_cordon/\">cordon</link> "
"the nodes before OS upgrades."
msgstr ""
"Sempre use o comando <link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_cordon/\""
">cordon</link> nos nós antes dos upgrades de sistema operacional."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1844 l10n/source/edge.xml:1962
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2352 l10n/source/edge.xml:2467
msgid ""
"Always upgrade <literal>control-plane</literal> nodes before "
"<literal>worker</literal> nodes."
msgstr ""
"Sempre faça upgrade dos nós do <literal>plano de controle</literal> antes "
"dos nós do <literal>worker</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1845 l10n/source/edge.xml:2353
msgid ""
"Always upgrade the cluster on a <emphasis role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> "
"node at a time basis."
msgstr ""
"Sempre faça upgrade do cluster <emphasis role=\"strong\">um</emphasis> nó de "
"cada vez."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1846 l10n/source/edge.xml:2354
msgid ""
"Once the <literal>OS SUC plans</literal> are deployed, the workflow looks "
"like this:"
msgstr ""
"Depois que os <literal>planos do SUC de sistema operacional</literal> forem "
"implantados, o fluxo de trabalho terá esta aparência:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1847 l10n/source/edge.xml:2355
msgid ""
"SUC reconciles the deployed <literal>OS SUC plans</literal> and creates a "
"<literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> on <emphasis role=\"strong\">each "
"node</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"O SUC reconcilia os <literal>planos do SUC de sistema operacional</literal> "
"implantados e cria um <literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> em <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">cada nó</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1848
msgid ""
"The <literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> creates a systemd.service (<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components-systemd-service\"/>) "
"for either package upgrade, or OS migration."
msgstr ""
"O <literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> cria um systemd.service (<xref linkend"
"=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components-systemd-service\"/>) para "
"upgrade de pacote ou migração de sistema operacional."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1849 l10n/source/edge.xml:2357
msgid ""
"The created <literal>systemd.service</literal> triggers the OS upgrade "
"process on the specific node."
msgstr ""
"O <literal>systemd.service</literal> criado aciona o processo de upgrade de "
"sistema operacional no nó específico."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1850 l10n/source/edge.xml:2358
msgid ""
"Once the OS upgrade process finishes, the corresponding node will be "
"<literal>rebooted</literal> to apply the updates on the system."
msgstr ""
"Após o término do processo de upgrade do sistema operacional, o nó "
"correspondente será <literal>reinicializado</literal> para aplicar as "
"atualizações ao sistema."

