#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3362
msgid ""
"The following sections show how to prepare the different scenarios for the "
"directed network provisioning workflow using SUSE Edge for Telco.  For "
"examples of the different configurations options for deployment "
"(incl. air-gapped environments, DHCP and DHCP-less networks, private "
"container registries, etc.), see the <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/atip/tree/release-3.3/telco-examples/edge-clusters\">SUSE "
"SUSE Edge for Telco repository</link>."
msgstr ""
"As seções a seguir mostram como preparar os diversos cenários para o fluxo "
"de trabalho de provisionamento de rede direcionado usando o SUSE Edge for "
"Telco. Para ver exemplos de opções de configurações diferentes para "
"implantação (incluindo ambientes air-gapped, redes DHCP e sem DHCP, "
"registros de contêiner particulares etc.), consulte o <link xl:href=\"https"
"://github.com/suse-edge/atip/tree/release-3.3/telco-examples/edge-clusters\""
">repositório SUSE do SUSE Edge for Telco</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3363
msgid "Prepare downstream cluster image for connected scenarios"
msgstr "Preparar uma imagem de cluster downstream para cenários conectados"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3364 l10n/source/edge.xml:3411
msgid ""
"Edge Image Builder (<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>) is used to prepare a "
"modified SLEMicro base image which is provisioned on downstream cluster "
"hosts."
msgstr ""
"O Edge Image Builder (<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>) é usado para "
"preparar uma imagem base do SLEMicro modificada que será provisionada aos "
"hosts de cluster downstream."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3365
msgid ""
"Much of the configuration via Edge Image Builder is possible, but in this "
"guide, we cover the minimal configurations necessary to set up the "
"downstream cluster."
msgstr ""
"Grande parte da configuração é possível pelo Edge Image Builder, mas neste "
"guia, abordamos as configurações mínimas necessárias para preparar o cluster "
"downstream."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3366
msgid "Prerequisites for connected scenarios"
msgstr "Pré-requisitos para cenários conectados"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3367 l10n/source/edge.xml:3414
msgid ""
"A container runtime such as <link "
"xl:href=\"https://podman.io\">Podman</link> or <link "
"xl:href=\"https://rancherdesktop.io\">Rancher Desktop</link> is required to "
"run Edge Image Builder."
msgstr ""
"É necessário um tempo de execução do contêiner, como <link xl:href="
"\"https://podman.io\">Podman</link> ou <link xl:href="
"\"https://rancherdesktop.io\">Rancher Desktop</link>, para executar o Edge "
"Image Builder."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3368 l10n/source/edge.xml:3415
msgid ""
"The base image will be built using the following guide <xref "
"linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> with the profile "
"<literal>Base-SelfInstall</literal> (or "
"<literal>Base-RT-SelfInstall</literal> for the Real-Time kernel). The "
"process is the same for both architectures (x86-64 and aarch64)."
msgstr ""
"A imagem base será criada conforme este guia <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-"
"builder-images\"/> com o perfil <literal>Base-SelfInstall</literal> (ou "
"<literal>Base-RT-SelfInstall</literal> para o kernel Real-Time). O processo "
"é o mesmo para as duas arquiteturas (x86-64 e aarch64)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3369 l10n/source/edge.xml:3416
msgid ""
"To deploy aarch64 downstream clusters, you must set before the management "
"cluster deployment the <literal>deployArchitecture: arm64</literal> "
"parameter in the <literal>metal3.yaml</literal> file explained in Management "
"Cluster Documentation (<xref linkend=\"arm64-mgmt-cluster\"/>). This is "
"required to ensure that the correct architecture is used for the downstream "
"cluster."
msgstr ""
"Para implantar clusters downstream aarch64, você deve definir o parâmetro "
"<literal>deployArchitecture: arm64</literal> no arquivo "
"<literal>metal3.yaml</literal> antes da implantação do cluster de "
"gerenciamento, o que está explicado na documentação sobre o cluster de "
"gerenciamento (<xref linkend=\"arm64-mgmt-cluster\"/>). Isso é necessário "
"para garantir o uso da arquitetura correta para o cluster downstream."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3370 l10n/source/edge.xml:3418
msgid ""
"It is required to use a build host with the same architecture of the images "
"being built. In other words, to build an <literal>aarch64</literal> image, "
"it is required to use an <literal>aarch64</literal> build host, and "
"vice-versa for <literal>x86-64</literal> (cross-builds are not supported at "
"this time)."
msgstr ""
"É necessário usar um host de build com a mesma arquitetura das imagens que "
"estão sendo criadas. Em outras palavras, para criar uma imagem "
"<literal>aarch64</literal>, é necessário usar um host de build "
"<literal>aarch64</literal>, e vice-versa para <literal>x86-64</literal> (não "
"há suporte para builds cruzados no momento)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3371
msgid "Image configuration for connected scenarios"
msgstr "Configuração da imagem para cenários conectados"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3374 l10n/source/edge.xml:3422
msgid ""
"The base image folder will contain the output raw image generated following "
"the guide <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> with the profile "
"<literal>Base-SelfInstall</literal> (or "
"<literal>Base-RT-SelfInstall</literal> for the Real-Time kernel) must be "
"copied/moved under the <literal>base-images</literal> folder."
msgstr ""
"A pasta da imagem base inclui a imagem bruta de saída gerada conforme o guia "
"<xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> com o perfil <literal>Base-"
"SelfInstall</literal> (ou <literal>Base-RT-SelfInstall</literal> para o "
"kernel Real-Time) e deve ser copiada/movida para a pasta <literal>base-"
"images</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3375 l10n/source/edge.xml:3423
msgid ""
"The <literal>network</literal> folder is optional, see <xref "
"linkend=\"add-network-eib\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"A pasta <literal>network</literal> é opcional. Consulte a <xref linkend"
"=\"add-network-eib\"/> para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3376 l10n/source/edge.xml:3424
