"Em que <literal>$SCC_REGISTRATION_CODE</literal> é o código de registro "
"copiado do <link xl:href=\"https://scc.suse.com/\">SUSE Customer Center</"
"link>, e a lista de pacotes inclui os pacotes mínimos usados nos perfis de "
"telecomunicações."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3403
msgid "Additional script for Advanced Network Configuration"
msgstr "Script adicional para configuração de rede avançada"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3404
msgid ""
"If you need to configure static IPs or more advanced networking scenarios as "
"described in <xref linkend=\"advanced-network-configuration\"/>, the "
"following additional configuration is required."
msgstr ""
"Se você precisa configurar IPs estáticos ou cenários de rede mais avançados, "
"conforme descrito na <xref linkend=\"advanced-network-configuration\"/>, a "
"configuração adicional abaixo é necessária."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3405
msgid ""
"In the <literal>network</literal> folder, create the following "
"<literal>configure-network.sh</literal> file - this consumes configuration "
"drive data on first-boot, and configures the host networking using the <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-configurator\">NM Configurator "
"tool</link>."
msgstr ""
"Na pasta <literal>network</literal>, crie o seguinte arquivo <literal"
">configure-network.sh</literal>, que consome os dados da unidade de "
"configuração na primeira inicialização e configura a rede do host usando a "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-configurator\">ferramenta NM "
"Configurator</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3408 l10n/source/edge.xml:3460
msgid ""
"This creates the output ISO image file named "
"<literal>eibimage-output-telco.raw</literal>, based on the definition "
"described above."
msgstr ""
"Esse procedimento cria o arquivo da imagem ISO de saída chamado <literal"
">eibimage-output-telco.raw</literal>, com base na definição descrita acima."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3409
