#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3556
msgid ""
"As you can see, the example shows the configuration to enable the interface "
"with static IPs, as well as the configuration to enable the VLAN using the "
"base interface, once the following variables are replaced with the actual "
"values, according to your infrastructure:"
msgstr ""
"Como você pode ver, o exemplo mostra a configuração para habilitar a "
"interface com os IPs estáticos e a VLAN usando a interface base, depois que "
"as seguintes variáveis são substituídas pelos valores reais, de acordo com a "
"sua infraestrutura:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3557
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal> — The control-plane interface "
"to be used for the edge cluster (for example, "
"<literal>eth0</literal>). Including <literal>identifier: "
"mac-address</literal> the naming is inspected automatically by the MAC "
"address so any interface name can be used."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal>: a interface do plano de "
"controle que será usada para o cluster Edge (por exemplo, "
"<literal>eth0</literal>). Incluindo o <literal>identifier: mac-address</"
"literal>, o endereço MAC inspeciona automaticamente a nomenclatura para que "
"qualquer nome de interface possa ser usado."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3558
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal> — The IP address to be used as an "
"endpoint for the edge cluster (must match with the kubeapi-server endpoint)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal>: o endereço IP usado como endpoint "
"para o cluster de borda (deve corresponder ao endpoint do servidor kubeapi)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3559
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal> — The CIDR to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>24</literal> if you want "
"<literal>/24</literal> or <literal>255.255.255.0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal>: o CIDR usado para o cluster de "
"borda (por exemplo, <literal>24</literal> para <literal>/24</literal> ou "
"<literal>255.255.255.0</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3560
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal> — The gateway to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>192.168.100.1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal>: o gateway usado para o cluster "
"de borda (por exemplo, <literal>192.168.100.1</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3561
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal> — The MAC address to be used for the "
"control-plane interface (for example, <literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal>: o endereço MAC usado para a "
"interface do plano de controle (por exemplo, "
"<literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3562
msgid ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal> — The DNS to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>192.168.100.2</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal>: o DNS usado para o cluster de borda (por "
"exemplo, <literal>192.168.100.2</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3563
msgid ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal> — The VLAN ID to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>100</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal>: o ID da VLAN usado para o cluster de borda ("
"por exemplo, <literal>100</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3564
