"<literal>${SRIOV-NIC-NAME1}</literal>: o nome da primeira interface "
"<literal>PF</literal> que será usada (por exemplo, <literal>eth0</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3603
msgid ""
