"After that, the easy way to upgrade is to export your current configurations "
"to a file, and then upgrade the "
"<literal>Metal<superscript>3</superscript></literal> version using that "
"previous file.  If any change is required in the new version, the file can "
"be edited before the upgrade."
msgstr ""
"Depois disso, a maneira fácil de fazer upgrade é exportar suas configurações "
"atuais para um arquivo e fazer upgrade da versão do "
"<literal>Metal<superscript>3</superscript></literal> usando o arquivo "
"anterior. Se for necessário alterar alguma coisa na nova versão, edite o "
"arquivo antes do upgrade."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3690
msgid "Downstream cluster upgrades"
msgstr "Upgrades de cluster downstream"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3691
msgid ""
"Upgrading downstream clusters involves updating several components. The "
"following sections cover the upgrade process for each of the components."
msgstr ""
"O upgrade de clusters downstream envolve a atualização de vários "
"componentes. As seções a seguir abordam o processo de upgrade de cada um "
"deles."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3692
msgid "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Upgrading the operating system</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fazendo upgrade do sistema operacional</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3693
msgid ""
"For this process, check the following reference (<xref "
"linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>) to build the new image with a new "
"operating system version.  With this new image generated by "
"<literal>EIB</literal>, the next provision phase uses the new operating "
"version provided.  In the following step, the new image is used to upgrade "
"the nodes."
msgstr ""
"Para este processo, consulte a seguinte referência (<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-"
"image-connected\"/>) para criar uma imagem com uma nova versão do sistema "
"operacional. Com essa imagem gerada pelo <literal>EIB</literal>, a próxima "
"fase de provisionamento usará a nova versão do sistema operacional "
"fornecida. Na etapa seguinte, a nova imagem será usada para fazer upgrade "
"dos nós."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3694
msgid "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Upgrading the RKE2 cluster</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fazendo upgrade do cluster RKE2</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3695
msgid ""
"The changes required to upgrade the <literal>RKE2</literal> cluster using "
"the automated workflow are the following:"
msgstr ""
"As alterações necessárias para fazer upgrade do cluster <literal>RKE2</"
"literal> usando o fluxo de trabalho automatizado são as seguintes:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3696
msgid ""
"Change the block <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> in the "
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal> shown in the following "
"section (<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\"/>):"
msgstr ""
"Altere o bloco <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> no <literal>capi-"
"provisioning-example.yaml</literal> mostrado na seguinte seção (<xref linkend"
"=\"single-node-provision\"/>):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3697
msgid "Specify the desired <literal>rolloutStrategy</literal>."
msgstr "Especifique a <literal>rolloutStrategy</literal> desejada."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3698
msgid ""
"Change the version of the <literal>RKE2</literal> cluster to the new version "
"replacing <literal>${RKE2_NEW_VERSION}</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Altere a versão do cluster <literal>RKE2</literal> para a nova versão, "
"substituindo <literal>${RKE2_NEW_VERSION}</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3699
msgid ""
"Change the block <literal>Metal3MachineTemplate</literal> in the "
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal> shown in the following "
"section (<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\"/>):"
msgstr ""
"Altere o bloco <literal>Metal3MachineTemplate</literal> no <literal>capi-"
"provisioning-example.yaml</literal> mostrado na seguinte seção (<xref linkend"
"=\"single-node-provision\"/>):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3700
msgid ""
"Change the image name and checksum to the new version generated in the "
"previous step."
msgstr ""
"Altere o nome e o checksum da imagem para a nova versão gerada na etapa "
"anterior."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3701
msgid ""
"Add the directive <literal>nodeReuse</literal> to <literal>true</literal> to "
"avoid creating a new node."
msgstr ""
"Adicione a diretiva <literal>nodeReuse</literal> a <literal>true</literal> "
"para evitar a criação de um novo nó."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3702
msgid ""
"Add the directive <literal>automatedCleaningMode</literal> to "
"<literal>metadata</literal> to enable the automated cleaning for the node."
msgstr ""
"Adicione a diretiva <literal>automatedCleaningMode</literal> a "
"<literal>metadata</literal> para habilitar a limpeza automatizada do nó."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
