#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3899
msgid ""
"In some cases when using a management cluster that has been upgraded from "
"Edge 3.2 to 3.3.0, downstream rolling upgrades via CAPI could result in "
"Machines stuck in Deleting state, this has been resolved via an update to "
"the RKE2 CAPI provider <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-provider-rke2/issues/661\">Upstream "
"RKE2 provider issue 661</link>"
msgstr ""
"Em alguns casos, ao usar um cluster de gerenciamento que foi atualizado do "
"Edge 3.2 para 3.3.0, os upgrades downstream contínuos feitos via CAPI podem "
"fazer com que as máquinas fiquem travadas no estado \"em exclusão\". Isso "
"foi resolvido com a atualização para o provedor CAPI RKE2 (<link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-provider-rke2/issues/661\">Upstream "
"RKE2 provider issue 661</link>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3900
msgid ""
"When configuring networking via nm-configurator, certain configurations "
"which identify interfaces by MAC in 3.3.0 did not work, this has been "
"resolved by updating NMC to 0.3.3 with corresponding updates to the EIB and "
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript> IPA downloader container images <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-configurator/issues/163\">Upstream "
"NM Configurator Issue</link>"
msgstr ""
"Ao configurar a rede pelo nm-configurator, algumas configurações que "
"identificam as interfaces por MAC na versão 3.3.0 não funcionavam, o que foi "
"resolvido ao atualizar o NMC para 0.3.3, com as atualizações correspondentes "
"nas imagens do contêiner do mecanismo de download IPA do EIB e do "
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript> <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/nm-configurator/issues/163\">Problema com o "
"NM Configurator upstream</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3901
msgid ""
"For long running Metal<superscript>3</superscript> management clusters in "
"3.3.0, it was possible for certificate expiry to cause the "
"baremetal-operator connection to ironic to fail, requiring a workaround of a "
"manual pod restart, this has been resolved via updates to the "
"Metal<superscript>3</superscript> chart <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/issues/178\">SUSE Edge charts "
"issue</link>"
msgstr ""
"Nos clusters de gerenciamento Metal<superscript>3</superscript> de longa "
"execução na versão 3.3.0, o vencimento do certificado poderia provocar falha "
"na conexão do operador bare metal com o Ironic, exigindo como solução "
"alternativa a reinicialização manual do pod, o que foi resolvido por meio de "
"atualizações no gráfico do Metal<superscript>3</superscript> <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/issues/178\">Problema nos gráficos do "
"SUSE Edge</link>"

