#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4019
msgid ""
"Updated Operating System to <link "
"xl:href=\"https://documentation.suse.com/sle-micro/6.1\">SUSE Linux Micro "
"6.1</link>"
msgstr ""
"Sistema operacional atualizado para o <link xl:href="
"\"https://documentation.suse.com/sle-micro/6.1\">SUSE Linux Micro 6.1</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4020
msgid "Updated Rancher Turtles, Cluster API and Metal3/Ironic versions"
msgstr ""
"Versões atualizadas do Rancher Turtles, da Cluster API e do Metal3/Ironic"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4021
msgid ""
"A container image is now provided which enables building updated SUSE Linux "
"Micro images. See <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Agora uma imagem do contêiner é fornecida para criar imagens atualizadas do "
"SUSE Linux Micro. Consulte o <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> "
"para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4022
msgid ""
"Deployment of AArch64 downstream clusters is now possible via the directed "
"network provisioning flow. See <xref "
"linkend=\"atip-automated-provisioning\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Agora a implantação de clusters downstream AArch64 é possível pelo fluxo de "
"provisionamento de rede direcionado. Consulte o <xref linkend=\"atip-"
"automated-provisioning\"/> para obter mais detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4023
msgid ""
"Deployment of dual-stack downstream clusters is now possible via the "
"directed network provisioning flow as a technology preview."
msgstr ""
"Agora a implantação de clusters downstream de pilha dupla é possível por "
"meio do fluxo de provisionamento de rede direcionado como prévia de "
"tecnologia."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4024
msgid ""
"Configuration of Precision Time Protocol (PTP) is now possible as a "
"technology preview. See <xref linkend=\"tech-previews\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Agora a configuração do Precision Time Protocol (PTP) é possível como prévia "
"de tecnologia. Consulte a <xref linkend=\"tech-previews\"/> para obter mais "
"detalhes."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4026
msgid ""
"Addresses <link "
"xl:href=\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-1974\">CVE-2025-1974</link> "
"with patches for ingress-nginx in RKE2. More information available <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/blog/2025/03/24/ingress-nginx-cve-2025-1974/\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"Endereços <link xl:href=\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-1974\""
">CVE-2025-1974</link> com patches para ingress-nginx no RKE2. Há mais "
"informações disponíveis <link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/blog/2025/03/24/ingress-nginx-cve-2025-1974/\""
">aqui</link>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4027
msgid "SUSE Storage (Longhorn) 1.8.1 contains several bugfixes, including"
msgstr "SUSE Storage (Longhorn) 1.8.1 com várias correções de bugs, incluindo:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4028
msgid ""
"Fix volume FailedMount issue which can cause volume attachment to fail <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/longhorn/longhorn/issues/9939\">Upstream "
"Longhorn Issue</link>"
msgstr ""
"Correção do problema de volume FailedMount que pode provocar falha no anexo "
"de volume <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/longhorn/longhorn/issues/9939\""
">Problema do Longhorn upstream</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4029
msgid ""
"Fix engine stuck in stopped state issue which can prevent volume attachment "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/longhorn/longhorn/issues/9938\">Upstream "
"Longhorn Issue</link>"
msgstr ""
"Correção do problema do mecanismo travado no estado parado que pode impedir "
"o anexo de volume <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/longhorn/longhorn/issues/9938\">Problema do Longhorn "
"upstream</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4030
msgid ""
"The Metal<superscript>3</superscript> chart update contains several "
"bugfixes, including"
msgstr ""
"A atualização do gráfico do Metal<superscript>3</superscript> contém várias "
"correções de bugs, incluindo:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4031
msgid ""
"A bug when deploying clusters with static IPs in networks with DHCP servers "
"has been resolved <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/196\">Upstream "
"Issue</link>"
msgstr ""
"Foi resolvido um bug ao implantar clusters com IPs estáticos nas redes com "
"servidores DHCP <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/charts/pull/196\">Problema upstream</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4032
msgid ""
"The MetalLB chart contains a fix to ensure downstream images are used when "
"frr-k8s is enabled"
msgstr ""
"O gráfico do MetalLB contém uma correção para garantir o uso das imagens "
"downstream quando frr-k8s estiver habilitado"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4033
msgid ""
"The Kiwi Builder has been updated to 10.2.12 to match recent security "
"changes in Kiwi, shifting from <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/OSInside/kiwi/commit/d4d39e481aaff8be28337a9c76c3913a8a482628\">md5 "
"to sha256 checksum methods</link> for image verification."
msgstr ""
"O construtor Kiwi foi atualizado para a versão 10.2.12 para se adequar às "
"alterações de segurança recentes no Kiwi, mudando dos <link xl:href=\"https"
"://github.com/OSInside/kiwi/commit/d4d39e481aaff8be28337a9c76c3913a8a482628\""
">métodos de checksum md5 para sha256</link> para verificação de imagens."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4034
msgid ""
"The Edge Image Builder image has been rebuilt to include the updated MetalLB "
"release and address the Kiwi changes, both mentioned above."
msgstr ""
"A imagem do Edge Image Builder foi recriada para incluir a versão atualizada "
"do MetalLB e abordar as alterações do Kiwi, ambas mencionadas acima."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4039
msgid ""
"In some cases when using a management cluster that has been upgraded from "
"Edge 3.2, downstream rolling upgrades via CAPI can result in Machines stuck "
"in Deleting state, this will be resolved via a future update <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-provider-rke2/issues/661\">Upstream "
"RKE2 provider issue 661</link>"
msgstr ""
"Em alguns casos, ao usar um cluster de gerenciamento que foi atualizado do "
"Edge 3.2, os upgrades downstream contínuos feitos via CAPI podem fazer com "
"que as máquinas fiquem travadas no estado \"em exclusão\". Isso será "
"resolvido com uma atualização futura (<link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/rancher/cluster-api-provider-rke2/issues/661\">Upstream "
"RKE2 provider issue 661</link>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4040
msgid ""
"When using RKE2 1.32.3, which resolves <link "
"xl:href=\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-1974\">CVE-2025-1974</link>, "
"SUSE Linux Micro 6.1 <emphasis role=\"strong\">must</emphasis> be updated to "
"include kernel <literal>&gt;=6.4.0-26-default</literal> or "
"<literal>&gt;=6.4.0-30-rt</literal> (real-time kernel) due to required "
"SELinux kernel patches. If not applied, the ingress-nginx pod will remain in "
"a <literal>CrashLoopBackOff</literal> state. To apply the kernel update run "
"<literal>transactional-update</literal> on the host itself (to update all "
"packages), or <literal>transactional-update pkg update "
"kernel-default</literal> (or kernel-rt) to update just the kernel, then "
"reboot the host. If deploying new clusters, please follow <xref "
"linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> to build fresh images containing "
"the latest kernel."
msgstr ""
"Ao usar o RKE2 1.32.3, que é resolvido como <link xl:href="
"\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2025-1974\">CVE-2025-1974</link>, o "
"SUSE Linux Micro 6.1 <emphasis role=\"strong\">deve</emphasis> ser "
"atualizado para incluir o kernel <literal>&gt;=6.4.0-26-default</literal> ou "
"<literal>&gt;=6.4.0-30-rt</literal> (kernel real-time) por causa dos patches "
"de kernel obrigatórios do SELinux. Se não forem aplicados, o pod ingress-"
"nginx continuará no estado <literal>CrashLoopBackOff</literal>. Para aplicar "
"a atualização do kernel, execute <literal>transactional-update</literal> no "
"próprio host (para atualizar todos os pacotes), ou <literal>transactional-"
"update pkg update kernel-default</literal> (ou kernel-rt) para atualizar "
"apenas o kernel e, em seguida, reinicialize o host. Se estiver implantando "
"novos clusters, siga o <xref linkend=\"guides-kiwi-builder-images\"/> para "
"criar novas imagens com o kernel mais recente."

